\f2\b\fs40 \cf2 \cb3 Versioning\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf2 \cb3 You must include the version at the top of your file inside the first curly brackets.\cb1 \
\cb3 There are currently no plans for changes that would require a version 4 in the foreseeable future. The recommendation is to use version 3.\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb3 \uc0\u9786 \u65039 
\f3\i  If you see me using version 2, then I have not had the time to update the resource.
\f1\i0 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa400\partightenfactor0

